                <head>No. 134.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Flores</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Personal.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington, D. C.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-07-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 4, 1885</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">To Secretary <hi rend="smallcaps">Bayard</hi>:</p>
                <p>With the announcement of amnesty I am directed to request that the Iroquois
                    should be altogether withdrawn even from the neighboring port of Payta, a
                    measure which I trust will prove of great mutual advantage. A prompt answer will
                    oblige.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FLORES.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
